    <title>Java Web例子</title>
    <url>/2023/11/25/java%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>#常用例子</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="常用例子"><a href="#常用例子" class="headerlink" title="常用例子"></a>常用例子</h1><h2 id="连接数据库"><a href="#连接数据库" class="headerlink" title="连接数据库"></a>连接数据库</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> Connection <span class="title function_">getConnection</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;		<span class="comment">//连接数据库</span></span><br><span class="line">		Connection conn= <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		String dbName=<span class="string">&quot;jdbc&quot;</span>;	<span class="comment">//数据库名字</span></span><br><span class="line">		String userName=<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>;	</span><br><span class="line">		String userPasswd=<span class="string">&quot;Mysqlroot1&quot;</span>;	</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">url</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;jdbc:mysql://localhost/&quot;</span>+ dbName +<span class="string">&quot;?characterEncoding=utf8&amp;serverTimezone=GMT%2B8&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			Class.forName(<span class="string">&quot;com.mysql.jdbc.Driver&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">			conn = DriverManager.getConnection(url,userName,userPasswd);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;<span class="keyword">catch</span>(Exception e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> conn;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="用户注册"><a href="#用户注册" class="headerlink" title="用户注册"></a>用户注册</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">checkZC</span><span class="params">(DataBean dataBean)</span> &#123;<span class="comment">//注册用户</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">flag</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">Connection</span> <span class="variable">conn</span> <span class="operator">=</span> getConnection();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">sql</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;select * from user where name=?&quot;</span>;			</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">PreparedStatement</span> <span class="variable">ps</span> <span class="operator">=</span> conn.prepareStatement(sql);</span><br><span class="line">			ps.setString(<span class="number">1</span>,dataBean.getName());</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">ResultSet</span> <span class="variable">rs</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ps.executeQuery();</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (rs.next()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				flag= -<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				rs.close();</span><br><span class="line">				ps.close();	</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				sql = <span class="string">&quot;insert into user values(?,?)&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				ps = conn.prepareStatement(sql);</span><br><span class="line">				ps.setString(<span class="number">1</span>, dataBean.getName());</span><br><span class="line">				ps.setString(<span class="number">2</span>,dataBean.getPass());</span><br><span class="line">				flag = ps.executeUpdate();				</span><br><span class="line">				ps.close();</span><br><span class="line">				</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			conn.close();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (SQLException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> flag;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="对应的servlet-页面"><a href="#对应的servlet-页面" class="headerlink" title="对应的servlet 页面"></a>对应的<code>servlet</code> 页面</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">DataBean</span> <span class="variable">data</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">DataBean</span>();</span><br><span class="line">		data.setName(request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">		data.setPass(request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;pass&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">ClassBean</span> <span class="variable">classBean</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ClassBean</span>(); </span><br><span class="line">		 <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">flag</span> <span class="operator">=</span> classBean.checkZC(data);</span><br><span class="line">		 <span class="keyword">if</span> (flag&gt;<span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			response.sendRedirect(<span class="string">&quot;./zc/zc_ok.jsp&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//成功页面</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			response.sendRedirect(<span class="string">&quot;./zc/zc_no.jsp&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//失败页面</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="用户登录"><a href="#用户登录" class="headerlink" title="用户登录"></a>用户登录</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">checklogin</span><span class="params">(DataBean dataBean)</span> &#123;<span class="comment">//登陆验证</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="variable">flag</span> <span class="operator">=</span><span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">Connection</span> <span class="variable">conn</span> <span class="operator">=</span> getConnection();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">sql</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;select * from user where name=? and pass=?&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">PreparedStatement</span> <span class="variable">ps</span> <span class="operator">=</span> conn.prepareStatement(sql);</span><br><span class="line">			ps.setString(<span class="number">1</span>, dataBean.getName());</span><br><span class="line">			ps.setString(<span class="number">2</span>, dataBean.getPass());</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">ResultSet</span> <span class="variable">rs</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ps.executeQuery();</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (rs.next()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				flag= <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			conn.close();</span><br><span class="line">			rs.close();</span><br><span class="line">			ps.close();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (SQLException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="comment">// <span class="doctag">TODO:</span> handle exception</span></span><br><span class="line">			e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> flag;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="对应servlet"><a href="#对应servlet" class="headerlink" title="对应servlet"></a>对应<code>servlet</code></h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">DataBean</span> <span class="variable">data</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">DataBean</span>();</span><br><span class="line">		data.setName(request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">		data.setPass(request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;pass&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">ClassBean</span> <span class="variable">classBean</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ClassBean</span>();</span><br><span class="line">		System.out.println(classBean.checklogin(data));</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (classBean.checklogin(data)) &#123; </span><br><span class="line">			response.sendRedirect(<span class="string">&quot;./login/Show.jsp&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			response.sendRedirect(<span class="string">&quot;./login/Login_no.jsp&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="输出所有用户信息"><a href="#输出所有用户信息" class="headerlink" title="输出所有用户信息"></a>输出所有用户信息</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> ArrayList&lt;DataBean&gt; <span class="title function_">getData</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;<span class="comment">//查找所有用户</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">PreparedStatement</span> <span class="variable">ps</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		ArrayList&lt;DataBean&gt; list = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;DataBean&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">Connection</span> <span class="variable">conn</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="built_in">this</span>.getConnection();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			ps = conn.prepareStatement(<span class="string">&quot;select * from user &quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="type">ResultSet</span> <span class="variable">rs</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ps.executeQuery();</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">while</span> (rs.next()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="type">DataBean</span> <span class="variable">data</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">DataBean</span>();</span><br><span class="line">				data.setName(rs.getString(<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">				data.setPass(rs.getString(<span class="string">&quot;pass&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">				list.add(data);</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		&#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (SQLException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> list;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="对应jsp"><a href="#对应jsp" class="headerlink" title="对应jsp"></a>对应<code>jsp</code></h3><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table border=<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;th&gt;用户名&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;th&gt;密码&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;jsp:useBean id=<span class="string">&quot;data&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;MyBean.ClassBean&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/jsp:useBean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">	ArrayList&lt;DataBean&gt; list = data.getData();</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span> ( <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; list.size(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">DataBean</span> <span class="variable">D</span> <span class="operator">=</span> list.get(i);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;th&gt;&lt;%=D.getName() %&gt;&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;th&gt;&lt;%=D.getPass() %&gt;&lt;/th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Java_web</category>
      </categories>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Flume 配置项</title>
    <url>/2023/11/14/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%B8%80%20Spark%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%EF%BC%9AStandalone%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="实验一-Spark安装部署：Standalone模式"><a href="#实验一-Spark安装部署：Standalone模式" class="headerlink" title="实验一 Spark安装部署：Standalone模式"></a>实验一 Spark安装部署：Standalone模式</h1><span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="实验步骤："><a href="#实验步骤：" class="headerlink" title="实验步骤："></a>实验步骤：</h2><h3 id="切换到spark-压缩包所在目录并将其解压到用户的根目录下："><a href="#切换到spark-压缩包所在目录并将其解压到用户的根目录下：" class="headerlink" title="切换到spark 压缩包所在目录并将其解压到用户的根目录下："></a>切换到spark 压缩包所在目录并将其解压到用户的根目录下：</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /home/zkpk/tgz/spark/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tar -zxvf spark-2.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz -C /home/zkpk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="进入用户根目录查看是否解压成功"><a href="#进入用户根目录查看是否解压成功" class="headerlink" title="进入用户根目录查看是否解压成功"></a>进入用户根目录查看是否解压成功</h3><p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114233955502.png" alt="image-20231114233955502"></p>
<h2 id="配置环境变量"><a href="#配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="配置环境变量"></a>配置环境变量</h2><h4 id="编辑环境变量配置文件，在末尾添加spark环境（安装路径）"><a href="#编辑环境变量配置文件，在末尾添加spark环境（安装路径）" class="headerlink" title="编辑环境变量配置文件，在末尾添加spark环境（安装路径）"></a>编辑环境变量配置文件，在末尾添加spark环境（安装路径）</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim .bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<blockquote>
<p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114234024117.png" alt="image-20231114234024117"></p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="重新加载配置文件，使其添加的环境变量生效。"><a href="#重新加载配置文件，使其添加的环境变量生效。" class="headerlink" title="重新加载配置文件，使其添加的环境变量生效。"></a>重新加载配置文件，使其添加的环境变量生效。</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source .bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="将其拷贝到slave01，slave02-上的-home-zkpk目录下"><a href="#将其拷贝到slave01，slave02-上的-home-zkpk目录下" class="headerlink" title="将其拷贝到slave01，slave02 上的&#x2F;home&#x2F;zkpk目录下"></a>将其拷贝到slave01，slave02 上的&#x2F;home&#x2F;zkpk目录下</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scp .bash_profile slave02:/home/zkpk/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="切换到slave01，slave02上重新加载配置文件"><a href="#切换到slave01，slave02上重新加载配置文件" class="headerlink" title="切换到slave01，slave02上重新加载配置文件"></a>切换到slave01，slave02上重新加载配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh  slave01</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">source  .bash_profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">exit 							#退出登入</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ssh slave02</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">source  .bash_profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">exit 						#退出登入</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="修改slaves文件"><a href="#修改slaves文件" class="headerlink" title="修改slaves文件"></a>修改slaves文件</h3><h4 id="进入spark配置文件目录，将conf-目录下的slaves-template文件重命名为slaves"><a href="#进入spark配置文件目录，将conf-目录下的slaves-template文件重命名为slaves" class="headerlink" title="进入spark配置文件目录，将conf 目录下的slaves.template文件重命名为slaves"></a>进入spark配置文件目录，将conf 目录下的slaves.template文件重命名为slaves</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /home/zkpk/spark-2.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7/conf/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mv slaves.template slaves</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="编辑slaves文件，将原来的内容替换为如下内容，并保存退出。"><a href="#编辑slaves文件，将原来的内容替换为如下内容，并保存退出。" class="headerlink" title="编辑slaves文件，将原来的内容替换为如下内容，并保存退出。"></a>编辑slaves文件，将原来的内容替换为如下内容，并保存退出。</h4><p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114234242143.png" alt="image-20231114234242143"></p>
<h3 id="修改conf目录中的spark-env-sh文件"><a href="#修改conf目录中的spark-env-sh文件" class="headerlink" title="修改conf目录中的spark-env.sh文件"></a>修改conf目录中的spark-env.sh文件</h3><h4 id="重命名文件spark-env-sh-template为spark-env-sh"><a href="#重命名文件spark-env-sh-template为spark-env-sh" class="headerlink" title="重命名文件spark-env.sh.template为spark-env.sh"></a>重命名文件spark-env.sh.template为spark-env.sh</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv spark-env.sh.template spark-env.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="编辑spark-env-sh文件，将以下内容添加到末尾"><a href="#编辑spark-env-sh文件，将以下内容添加到末尾" class="headerlink" title="编辑spark-env.sh文件，将以下内容添加到末尾"></a>编辑spark-env.sh文件，将以下内容添加到末尾</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim spark-env.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>内容如下:</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114234358587.png" alt="image-20231114234358587"></p>
<h3 id="将经过配置的spark主目录远程拷贝到另外两个从节点slave01和slave02"><a href="#将经过配置的spark主目录远程拷贝到另外两个从节点slave01和slave02" class="headerlink" title="将经过配置的spark主目录远程拷贝到另外两个从节点slave01和slave02"></a>将经过配置的spark主目录远程拷贝到另外两个从节点slave01和slave02</h3><h4 id="切换到用户根目录，远程拷贝到slave01，slave02-的同目录上"><a href="#切换到用户根目录，远程拷贝到slave01，slave02-的同目录上" class="headerlink" title="切换到用户根目录，远程拷贝到slave01，slave02 的同目录上"></a>切换到用户根目录，远程拷贝到slave01，slave02 的同目录上</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scp -r spark-2.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7/ zkpk@slave01:/home/zkpk/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">scp -r spark-2.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7/ zkpk@slave02:/home/zkpk/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="启动spark集群"><a href="#启动spark集群" class="headerlink" title="启动spark集群"></a>启动spark集群</h3><h4 id="进入master节点-的spark的sbin目录"><a href="#进入master节点-的spark的sbin目录" class="headerlink" title="进入master节点 的spark的sbin目录"></a>进入master节点 的spark的sbin目录</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd spark-2.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7/sbin/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="运行start-all-sh启动spark集群，然后分别在master、slave01和slave02上使用jps命令查看进程，分别出现master和worker进程，说明集群启动成功"><a href="#运行start-all-sh启动spark集群，然后分别在master、slave01和slave02上使用jps命令查看进程，分别出现master和worker进程，说明集群启动成功" class="headerlink" title="运行start-all.sh启动spark集群，然后分别在master、slave01和slave02上使用jps命令查看进程，分别出现master和worker进程，说明集群启动成功"></a>运行start-all.sh启动spark集群，然后分别在master、slave01和slave02上使用jps命令查看进程，分别出现master和worker进程，说明集群启动成功</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./start-all.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114234502727.png" alt="image-20231114234502727"></p>
<h3 id="验证spark-standalone模式部署正确"><a href="#验证spark-standalone模式部署正确" class="headerlink" title="验证spark standalone模式部署正确"></a>验证spark standalone模式部署正确</h3><h4 id="在master节点菜单”Application”中-打开浏览器访问spark-webui界面地址：http-master-8080，出现类似下图界面"><a href="#在master节点菜单”Application”中-打开浏览器访问spark-webui界面地址：http-master-8080，出现类似下图界面" class="headerlink" title="在master节点菜单”Application”中 打开浏览器访问spark webui界面地址：http://master:8080，出现类似下图界面:"></a>在master节点菜单”Application”中 打开浏览器访问spark webui界面地址：<a href="http://master:8080，出现类似下图界面">http://master:8080，出现类似下图界面</a>:</h4><p><img src="/./../images/image-20231114234529689.png" alt="image-20231114234529689"></p>
<h3 id="命令行提交job到spark集群"><a href="#命令行提交job到spark集群" class="headerlink" title="命令行提交job到spark集群"></a>命令行提交job到spark集群</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./bin/spark-submit --class org.apache.spark.examples.SparkPi --master spark://master:7077 --num-executors 3 --driver-memory 1g --executor-memory 1g --executor-cores 1 examples/jars/spark-examples_2.11-2.1.1.jar 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



